{"tid":953865,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸外賣員被取消訂單留下男兒淚 美團外賣特別獎勵千元「委屈獎」","createTime":"2018-12-24T08:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T09:05:47.000Z","uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce6cd295975c67cc59e465d49c1df90bd97addf","tid":953865,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T08:53:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2236045\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2236045&d=6fMl2OqFzk%2F0zp%2Fps%2FGrtRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=02238b4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2236045</a><br />\n<br />\n香港現時外賣 apps 的選擇愈來愈多，而在大陸外賣 apps 的使用更加流行。外賣 apps 平台獲得成功，背後必須依賴大批外賣員辛苦工作，準時送出外賣訂單。最近微博上流傳影片，影片中外賣送餐員在等候外賣期間，突然在手機上看到訂單被客人取消的消息，忍不住留下男兒淚......<br />\n<br />\n目前中國內地在外賣 apps 公司任職的外賣送餐員，其收入普遍按接單數量計算。按照送餐時間和外賣員級別而異，外賣員每完成每張包括買餐及送餐委託的訂單，只能獲得 3.5 人民幣至 5 人民幣（折合約 HK$3.97 至 HK$5.67）的報酬。一旦被客人負評或取消訂單，更有可能會被罸款，損失整天大部分收入。<br />\n=================================================<br />\n慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef7c7bedb7a559e56bb99e18f47f0a05c990621","tid":953865,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T08:54:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f456a2ffe63b0a5dc00535054c261e0cceaf3c0","tid":953865,"uid":48702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T08:56:57.000Z","msg":"新聞一出之後肯定好多人會自己製造被取消單"},{"pid":"7bd6ce8833882fa255671c153548d1500dc7e801","tid":953865,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T09:00:01.000Z","msg":"香港做唔起嘅原因？得咁少錢"},{"pid":"16cf088121a776cb7881715dd58af079b12a6f85","tid":953865,"uid":10757,"like":0,"disl